    "_postman_id": "a4c7a4b4-0000-0000-0000-auth-collection",
    "description": "用于测试后端注册与登录接口（USER 注册、OWNER 注册，USER/OWNER/ADMIN 登录）。基础地址为 http://localhost:9999/sportsVenue。",
